room_title: Escape room "Corporation of D.O.O.M" by Escape Rooms HQ in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: It was amazing! There were a bunch of puzzles and hieroglyphs which took our group a while to figure out.. but overall we had a great time !

room_title: Escape room "Corporation of D.O.O.M" by Escape Rooms HQ in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: We did the Corporation of DOOM episode at the Irving location today. It was super cool... packed with puzzles and hieroglyphs and fun effects. We will definitely be back to do more episodes!

room_title: Escape room "Corporation of D.O.O.M" by Escape Rooms HQ in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: First time in an escape room - this place exceeded my expectations. Corporation of Doom was fun. Will be back for the other rooms!
